the fear he inspired in the heart of the weak.

Tyrael: I think Kaiser didn't yet. I have to request your
authorization for an experiment I am conducting. I have used data from
a Predacon engine computer and the DNA of one of my late warrior and I
might have discovered a way to devellop the greatest warrior ever. I
need a protoform to apply this now. Also, Darkangel can assist me. Do
you allow me to go on?
